 《最后的晚宴》首张专辑取得九年来最高的第一名https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-score-biggest-number-one-debut-album-in-nine-years-3585175?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=the-最后的晚餐派对九年来最高首张专辑第一名Liberty DunworthFri, 09 Feb 2024 17:45:30 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3585175 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/The-Last-Dinner-Party@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="最后的晚宴派对在庆祝他们的首张排名第一专辑“Prelude to Ecstasy”时与他们的官方排名第一奖合影" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/The-Last-Dinner-Party@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/The-Last-Dinner-Party@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/The-Last-Dinner-Party@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/The-Last-Dinner-Party@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/The-Last-Dinner-Party@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/The-Last-Dinner-Party@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这是自 Years &amp; Years 2015 年专辑《Communion》以来首张专辑开张最盛大的一周</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-score-biggest-number-one-debut-album-in-nine-years-3585175">《最后的晚宴》 (The Last Evening Party) 成为九年来最高的首张专辑，</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/The-Last-Dinner-Party@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="最后的晚宴派对在庆祝他们的首张排名第一专辑“Prelude to Ecstasy”时与他们的官方排名第一奖合影" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/The-Last-Dinner-Party@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/The-Last-Dinner-Party@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/The-Last-Dinner-Party@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/The-Last-Dinner-Party@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/The-Last-Dinner-Party@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/The-Last-Dinner-Party@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">最后的晚餐派对</a>凭借突破性的唱片<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-last-dinner-party-prelude-to-ecstasy-album-review-radar-3577784">“Prelude To Ecstasy”</a>获得了近十年来最大的首张专辑第一名。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-cover/the-cover-the-last-dinner-party-interview-prelude-to-ecstasy-3552625">最后的晚宴：巴洛克流行音乐的新加冕君主</a></strong></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/the-last-dinner-party-prelude-to-ecstasy-debut-number-1-album/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">官方排行榜公司</a>今天宣布了这一具有里程碑意义的消息，该公司证实，这支冉冉升起的独立摇滚乐队凭借首张专辑在短短一周内就赢得了 32,800 个榜单单位。</p><p>这是近十年来乐队登顶首张专辑最盛大的首周。在此之前， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/olly-alexander">Olly Alexander</a>领导的乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/years-and-years">Years &amp; Years</a>也创下了首张 LP &#39;Communion&#39; 销量 55,000 张的里程碑。</p><p>由阿比盖尔·莫里斯 (Abigail Morris)、莉齐·梅兰 (Lizzie Mayland)、艾米丽·罗伯茨 (Emily Roberts)、乔治亚·戴维斯 (Georgia Davies) 和奥罗拉·尼舍夫奇 (Aurora Nishevci) 组成的五人组合于上周（2 月 2 日）发行了《Prelude To Ecstasy》，并在唱片中取得了其他一些令人印象深刻的成就。</p><p>其中包括本周该专辑成为英国独立唱片店最畅销的专辑，并继续在官方唱片店排行榜上占据第一名。更重要的是，它也成为本周最畅销的黑胶唱片，销量超过 14,000 张，这是自去年 11 月<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">Oasis</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-announce-25th-anniversary-reissue-of-the-masterplan-b-sides-collection-3500933">重新发行的《The Masterplan》</a>上架以来的最高数字。 </p><figure id="attachment_3585180" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3585180" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3585180" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/The-Last-Dinner-Party-1@2000x1270.jpg" alt="最后的晚宴派对在庆祝他们的首张排名第一专辑“Prelude to Ecstasy”时与他们的官方排名第一奖合影" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/The-Last-Dinner-Party-1@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/The-Last-Dinner-Party-1@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/The-Last-Dinner-Party-1@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/The-Last-Dinner-Party-1@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/The-Last-Dinner-Party-1@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/The-Last-Dinner-Party-1@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3585180" class="wp-caption-text">最后的晚宴派对在庆祝他们的首张排名第一专辑“Prelude to Ecstasy”时与他们的官方排名第一奖合影（来源：官方排行榜）</figcaption></figure><p>在专辑排行榜上的其他地方，利物浦歌手兼作曲家<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jamie-webster">杰米·韦伯斯特 (Jamie Webster)</a>凭借上周发行的《10 For The People》和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift</a> ) 的几张专辑，第三次跻身前十名，也是迄今为止排名最高的专辑。继她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-announces-new-album-the-tortured-poets-department-3582273">在格莱美奖上宣布《The Tortured Poets Department》</a>后，她的专辑重新进入排行榜。</p><p> <em>NME</em>的 Sophie Williams <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-last-dinner-party-prelude-to-ecstasy-album-review-radar-3577784">给予《Prelude To Ecstasy》四星好评</a>，她形容这张专辑包含“足够的自信和吸引力，使他们与之前的专辑有所不同”。</p><p> “有些人可能会选择将乐队的成功视为对他们在早期职业生涯中受到的严格审查的解毒剂，这些审查包括他们的崛起、外表以及在没有‘严肃’意图的情况下制作音乐的决定。但如果把所有这些都拿走，你仍然会留下易于接受和返回的精彩歌曲。很难错过他们正在做的所有正确的事情，”它补充道。</p><p>该乐队目前是<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-cover/the-cover-the-last-dinner-party-interview-prelude-to-ecstasy-3552625"><em>NME</em>一月/二月印刷版的最新封面明星</a>，并向我们介绍了他们职业生涯的开始，以及他们与众不同的原因。 </p><figure id="attachment_3552661" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3552661" style="width: 1990px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3552661" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/NME-COVER-THE-LAST-DINNER-PARTY-COVER-CREDIT-PHOEBE-FOX@1990x2488.jpg" alt="《最后的晚宴》 NME 封面" width="1990" height="2488" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/NME-COVER-THE-LAST-DINNER-PARTY-COVER-CREDIT-PHOEBE-FOX@1990x2488.jpg 1990w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/NME-COVER-THE-LAST-DINNER-PARTY-COVER-CREDIT-PHOEBE-FOX@1990x2488-400x500.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/NME-COVER-THE-LAST-DINNER-PARTY-COVER-CREDIT-PHOEBE-FOX@1990x2488-800x1000.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/NME-COVER-THE-LAST-DINNER-PARTY-COVER-CREDIT-PHOEBE-FOX@1990x2488-696x870.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/NME-COVER-THE-LAST-DINNER-PARTY-COVER-CREDIT-PHOEBE-FOX@1990x2488-1392x1740.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/NME-COVER-THE-LAST-DINNER-PARTY-COVER-CREDIT-PHOEBE-FOX@1990x2488-1068x1335.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1990px) 100vw, 1990px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3552661" class="wp-caption-text"> NME 封面上的最后晚宴。图片来源：NME 的菲比·福克斯</figcaption></figure><p>“我们花了很长时间发布了任何东西，这在某种程度上是故意的”，戴维斯说。 “这是关于整体的体验，而不是来自单身人士的即时认可。”</p><p> “我们知道我们与其他从事后朋克风格的乐队不同，”她继续说道，莫里斯补充道。 “我们想象了外出时希望看到的那种快乐、激动人心的表演，并据此创建了我们自己的‘梦想乐队’。”</p><p>在《最后的晚宴派对》的其他新闻中，本周早些时候，该乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-the-last-dinner-party-cover-troye-sivans-one-of-your-girls-in-the-radio-1-live-lounge-nme-radar-3583280">在 Radio 1 Live Lounge 翻唱了 Troye Sivan 的《One Of Your Girls》，</a>并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-add-three-shows-to-2024-uk-and-ireland-tour-due-to-phenomenal-demand-3584408">因需求旺盛而在 2024 年英国和爱尔兰巡演中增加了三场演出</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-score-biggest-number-one-debut-album-in-nine-years-3585175">《最后的晚宴》 (The Last Evening Party) 成为九年来最高的首张专辑，</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 《另一轮》导演分享对克里斯·洛克翻拍的看法：“如果是狗屎，他会再次被打耳光” https://www.nme.com/news/film/another-round-director-shares-thoughts-on-chris-rock-remake-if-its-shit-hell-get-slapped-again-3585165?utm_source= rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=另一轮导演分享关于克里斯摇滚重拍的想法，如果它是狗屎地狱，再次被打耳光Chris EdwardsFri, 09 Feb 2024 17:13:01 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3585165 <p><img width="2042" height="1388" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Thomas-Vinterberg-and-Chris-Rock.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Thomas-Vinterberg-and-Chris-Rock.jpg 2042w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Thomas-Vinterberg-and-Chris-Rock-400x272.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Thomas-Vinterberg-and-Chris-Rock-800x544.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Thomas-Vinterberg-and-Chris-Rock-696x473.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Thomas-Vinterberg-and-Chris-Rock-1392x946.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Thomas-Vinterberg-and-Chris-Rock-1068x726.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2042px) 100vw, 2042px" /></p><p> “看到他的想法真是令人兴奋”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/another-round-director-shares-thoughts-on-chris-rock-remake-if-its-shit-hell-get-slapped-again-3585165">《另一轮》导演分享了对克里斯·洛克翻拍的想法：“如果是狗屎，他会再次被打耳光”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2042" height="1388" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Thomas-Vinterberg-and-Chris-Rock.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Thomas-Vinterberg-and-Chris-Rock.jpg 2042w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Thomas-Vinterberg-and-Chris-Rock-400x272.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Thomas-Vinterberg-and-Chris-Rock-800x544.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Thomas-Vinterberg-and-Chris-Rock-696x473.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Thomas-Vinterberg-and-Chris-Rock-1392x946.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Thomas-Vinterberg-and-Chris-Rock-1068x726.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2042px) 100vw, 2042px" /></p><p> <em>《另一回合》</em>导演托马斯·温特伯格分享了他对<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chris-rock">克里斯·洛克</a>执导的美国翻拍片的看法。</p><p>温特伯格在接受丹麦出版物<a href="https://soundvenue.com/film/2024/02/thomas-vinterberg-joker-med-chris-rocks-druk-remake-hvis-han-laver-noget-lort-saa-faar-han-en-flad-mere-557243" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Ekstra Bladet</em></a>采访时表示，他很高兴看到洛克在这部 2021 年奥斯卡获奖剧集中的表现。</p><p> “克里斯·洛克的选择令人兴奋。 [看到]他的想法令人兴奋。我充满了美好的期待。”</p><p>温特伯格没有透露他是否以任何方式参与了美国版的翻拍，但他确实向洛克发出了警告。</p><p> “如果是狗屎的话，他会再次被打耳光，”他说。</p><p>温特伯格当然指的是 2022 年奥斯卡颁奖典礼上发生的臭名昭著的事件，当时<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/will-smith-has-resigned-from-the-academy-says-he-will-accept-any-further-consequences-3196231">威尔·史密斯走上舞台，</a>因为洛克拿他的妻子贾达·萍克·史密斯开玩笑而扇了洛克一巴掌。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="又一轮|官方预告片|麦斯·米科尔森主演" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/40X5EX6Us7c?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>斯图尔特·布隆伯格 (Stuart Bloomberg) 撰写了美国版<em>《另一轮》</em>的初稿，据报道，另一位作家已受聘与洛克合作。</p><p>温特伯格的版本由麦斯·米科尔森、托马斯·博·拉森、马格努斯·米兰和拉尔斯·兰特主演，饰演四名高中教师，他们测试了一定酒精含量可以提高创造力和幸福感的理论。他们一起决定通过在整个工作日保持恒定的醉酒程度来进行实验。</p><p> 2021 年， <em>《另一回合》</em>在奥斯卡颁奖典礼上获得成功并荣获最佳国际电影奖后，该片的版权被出售给了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/leonardo-dicaprio">莱昂纳多·迪卡普里奥</a>的制作公司 Appian Way。</p><p>这自然引发了迪卡普里奥将在影片中扮演主角的猜测，但目前尚未做出选角决定。</p><p>据报道， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/chris-rock-reportedly-teams-up-with-steven-spielberg-for-new-martin-luther-king-biopic-3511163">洛克将与史蒂文·斯皮尔伯格合作拍摄一部新的马丁·路德·金传记片</a>。</p><p>据<a class="body-link css-xw41s5 et3p2gv0" href="https://variety.com/2023/film/news/chris-rock-martin-luther-king-jr-biopic-steven-spielberg-1235746488/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-vars-ga-outbound-link="https://variety.com/2023/film/news/chris-rock-martin-luther-king-jr-biopic-steven-spielberg-1235746488/" data-vars-ga-ux-element="Hyperlink" data-vars-ga-call-to-action="Variety"><em>Variety 报道</em></a>，洛克正在就导演和制作改编自作家乔纳森·艾格的传记<em>《国王：一生》的事宜进行最后谈判，</em>而斯皮尔伯格将担任该项目的执行制片人。环球影业被认为将参与这部电影的拍摄。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/another-round-director-shares-thoughts-on-chris-rock-remake-if-its-shit-hell-get-slapped-again-3585165">《另一轮》导演分享了对克里斯·洛克翻拍的想法：“如果是狗屎，他会再次被打耳光”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
